title: OpenAI launches AI shopping tool in ChatGPT ahead of Thanksgiving
description: OpenAI has introduced a new AI-powered shopping feature in ChatGPT designed to help users research and compare products ahead of the Thanksgiving holiday. The feature, called shopping research, is rolling out on mobile and web for users across Free, Go, Plus, and Pro plans, with nearly unlimited usage available through the holiday season.
